/ =================================================================
/ BUSCAMINAS 16x16 вЂ” display MARIE
/ Minas: 3 | Inputs por turno: fila, col, accion(1=revelar 2=bandera)
/ val original=oculta | val+100=descubierta | val+200=bandera
/ Score: movimientos totales (revelar + banderas)
/ =================================================================

        ORG 000

/ в”Ђв”Ђ FASE 1: Pintar todo el display de gris oscuro в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Load  DispBase
        Store Ptr
        LoadImmi 0FF
        Store Cnt
PintaG, Load  Gris
        StoreI Ptr
        Load  Ptr
        Add   Uno
        Store Ptr
        Load  Cnt
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  DecrG
        Jump  PintaT

/ в”Ђв”Ђ FASE 1b: Inicializar tablero en 0 в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Load  TablBase
        Store Ptr
        LoadImmi 0FF
        Store Cnt
PintaT, Load  Cero
        StoreI Ptr
        Load  Ptr
        Add   Uno
        Store Ptr
        Load  Cnt
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  DecrT
        JnS   ColocarMinas     / tablero listo в†’ colocar minas

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Turno: outputs de guia + leer fila, columna, accion в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
Turno,  JnS   PrintMsgMov  / OUTPUT: 'Movs:'
        JnS   ImprimirNum  / OUTPUT: numero de movimientos en ASCII
        Load  CharNL
        Output             / salto de linea tras el numero
        JnS   PrintMsgFila / OUTPUT: 'Fila:'
        Input              / fila (1-16)
        Subt  Uno
        Store FilaIn
        JnS   PrintMsgCol  / OUTPUT: 'Col:'
        Input              / columna (1-16)
        Subt  Uno
        Store ColIn
        JnS   PrintMsgAcc  / OUTPUT: 'Acc:'
        Input              / accion: 1=revelar, 2=bandera
        Store Accion

/ в”Ђв”Ђ idx = fila*16 + col в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Load  FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   FilaIn
        Add   ColIn
        Store Idx

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Punteros a tablero y display в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Add   TablBase
        Store TablPtr
        Load  Idx
        Add   DispBase
        Store DispPtr

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Leer valor actual de tablero[Idx] в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        LoadI TablPtr
        Store ValCelda

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Detectar estado de celda por color del display в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        LoadI DispPtr      / AC = color actual de la celda
        Subt  Gris         / AC = color - Gris
        SkipCond 400       / si ==0 в†’ es gris в†’ oculta sin bandera
        Jump  NoEsGris     / no es gris
        Jump  ChkAccion    / oculta sin bandera в†’ verificar accion
NoEsGris, LoadI DispPtr    / recargar color
        Subt  Amarillo     / AC = color - Amarillo
        SkipCond 400       / si ==0 в†’ tiene bandera
        Jump  Turno        / otro color в†’ celda descubierta, ignorar

/ в”Ђв”Ђ ChkBandera: celda con bandera в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
ChkBandera, Load Accion
        Subt  Uno          / AC = Accion - 1
        SkipCond 400       / si AC==0 в†’ Accion=1 в†’ bloquear
        Jump  ChkTogBand   / Accion=2 в†’ togglear bandera
        JnS   PrintMsgBand / OUTPUT: 'NoBand!' (sin contar mov)
        Jump  Turno        / Accion=1 con bandera в†’ ignorar

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Toggle bandera в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
ChkTogBand, LoadI DispPtr  / AC = color actual de la celda en display
        Subt  Amarillo     / AC = color - Amarillo
        SkipCond 400       / si AC==0 в†’ ya tiene bandera в†’ quitar
        Jump  PonerBandera / color != amarillo в†’ poner bandera

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Quitar bandera в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Load  ValCelda
        Subt  MarcaBand    / val - 200 = valor original
        StoreI TablPtr     / restaurar en tablero
        Load  Gris
        StoreI DispPtr     / volver a gris oscuro
        Jump  ContarMov    / contar movimiento

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Poner bandera в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
PonerBandera, Load ValCelda
        Add   MarcaBand    / val + 200
        StoreI TablPtr
        Load  Amarillo
        StoreI DispPtr
        Jump  ContarMov    / contar movimiento

/ в”Ђв”Ђ ChkAccion: celda oculta sin bandera в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
ChkAccion, Load Accion
        Subt  Uno          / AC = Accion - 1
        SkipCond 400       / si AC==0 в†’ Accion=1 в†’ revelar
        Jump  PonerBandera / Accion=2 в†’ poner bandera
        Jump  Descubrir

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Descubrir в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
Descubrir, LoadI DispPtr   / leer color de la celda
        Subt  Amarillo     / es bandera?
        SkipCond 400       / si ==0 в†’ tiene bandera в†’ ignorar
        Jump  ChkMina      / no tiene bandera в†’ continuar
        Jump  Turno        / tiene bandera в†’ no revelar, no contar
ChkMina, Load ValCelda
        Add   Uno          / si val=-1 в†’ AC=0
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  NoesMina

/ в”Ђв”Ђ ES MINA: revelar todas las minas en negro + Halt в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Load  TablBase
        Store Ptr
        Load  DispBase
        Store DispPtr2
        LoadImmi 0FF
        Store Cnt
RevMin, LoadI Ptr
        Store ValTemp
        Add   Uno          / mina original: val=-1 в†’ AC=0
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  ChkMinaBand
        Load  Negro
        StoreI DispPtr2    / mina в†’ negro
        Jump  AvanzaRev
ChkMinaBand, Load ValTemp
        Subt  MinaBand     / AC = val - 199
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  AvanzaRev
        Load  Negro
        StoreI DispPtr2    / mina con bandera в†’ negro
AvanzaRev, Load Ptr
        Add   Uno
        Store Ptr
        Load  DispPtr2
        Add   Uno
        Store DispPtr2
        Load  Cnt
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  DecrR
        JnS   PrintMsgPierde / OUTPUT: 'Perdiste'
        Load  Movimientos
        Output             / score final al perder
        Load  CharNL
        Output
        Halt               / FIN: perdiste

/ в”Ђв”Ђ ColocarMinas: ROMBO de minas en tablero в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
/ Entradas via Input:
/   1) fila centro  (1-16, se convierte a 0-indexed)
/   2) col  centro  (1-16, se convierte a 0-indexed)
/   3) radio        (1-7, distancia Manhattan desde el centro al borde)
/ El rombo son todos los puntos con |dr| + |dc| == radio.
/ Se recorren las 4 diagonales desde los 4 vertices cardinales.
/ Total minas = 4 * radio (excepto radio=1 que son 4 puntos).
/ =======================================================================

ColocarMinas, HEX 0        / slot retorno JnS

/ --- Leer entradas ---
        Input
        Subt  Uno
        Store FilaIn           / centro fila, 0-indexed
        Input
        Subt  Uno
        Store ColIn            / centro col,  0-indexed
        Input
        Store DIAM             / radio Manhattan (1-7)

/ --- Validar FilaIn (0-15) ---
        Load  FilaIn
        SkipCond 000
        Jump  DFilaGE0
        Jump  MineEnd
DFilaGE0, Load FilaIn
        Subt  Quince
        SkipCond 800
        Jump  DFilaOK
        Jump  MineEnd

/ --- Validar ColIn (0-15) ---
DFilaOK, Load  ColIn
        SkipCond 000
        Jump  DColGE0
        Jump  MineEnd
DColGE0, Load  ColIn
        Subt  Quince
        SkipCond 800
        Jump  DColOK
        Jump  MineEnd

/ --- Validar DIAM >= 1 ---
DColOK, Load  DIAM
        SkipCond 800
        Jump  MineEnd
        Load  DIAM
        Subt  Siete
        SkipCond 800
        Jump  DDiamOK
        Jump  MineEnd

/ =======================================================================
/ Rombo: 4 lados. Cada lado recorre DIAM pasos.
/ Vertices cardinales:
/   Norte: (FilaIn-DIAM, ColIn)
/   Sur:   (FilaIn+DIAM, ColIn)
/   Este:  (FilaIn,      ColIn+DIAM)
/   Oeste: (FilaIn,      ColIn-DIAM)
/ Lados:
/   Norteв†’Este:  dr=+1, dc=+1   (DIAM-1 puntos, sin incluir vertices)
/   Esteв†’Sur:    dr=+1, dc=-1
/   Surв†’Oeste:   dr=-1, dc=-1
/   Oesteв†’Norte: dr=-1, dc=+1
/ Pintamos los 4 vertices y luego los 4 lados sin repetir vertices.
/ =======================================================================

/ --- Pintar vertice Norte ---
DDiamOK, Load  FilaIn
        Subt  DIAM
        Store PR
        Load  ColIn
        Store PC
        JnS   PintarPunto

/ --- Pintar vertice Sur ---
        Load  FilaIn
        Add   DIAM
        Store PR
        Load  ColIn
        Store PC
        JnS   PintarPunto

/ --- Pintar vertice Este ---
        Load  FilaIn
        Store PR
        Load  ColIn
        Add   DIAM
        Store PC
        JnS   PintarPunto

/ --- Pintar vertice Oeste ---
        Load  FilaIn
        Store PR
        Load  ColIn
        Subt  DIAM
        Store PC
        JnS   PintarPunto

/ =======================================================================
/ Lado Norteв†’Este: desde Norte, dr=+1 dc=+1, DIAM-1 pasos
/ =======================================================================
        Load  FilaIn
        Subt  DIAM
        Store DCurR
        Load  ColIn
        Store DCurC
        Load  DIAM
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt

DNELp,  Load  Cnt
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  DNEDo
        Jump  DNEEnd
DNEDo,  Load  DCurR
        Add   Uno
        Store DCurR
        Store PR
        Load  DCurC
        Add   Uno
        Store DCurC
        Store PC
        JnS   PintarPunto
        Load  Cnt
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt
        Jump  DNELp

/ =======================================================================
/ Lado Esteв†’Sur: desde Este, dr=+1 dc=-1, DIAM-1 pasos
/ =======================================================================
DNEEnd, Load  FilaIn
        Store DCurR
        Load  ColIn
        Add   DIAM
        Store DCurC
        Load  DIAM
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt

DESLp,  Load  Cnt
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  DESDo
        Jump  DESEnd
DESDo,  Load  DCurR
        Add   Uno
        Store DCurR
        Store PR
        Load  DCurC
        Subt  Uno
        Store DCurC
        Store PC
        JnS   PintarPunto
        Load  Cnt
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt
        Jump  DESLp

/ =======================================================================
/ Lado Surв†’Oeste: desde Sur, dr=-1 dc=-1, DIAM-1 pasos
/ =======================================================================
DESEnd, Load  FilaIn
        Add   DIAM
        Store DCurR
        Load  ColIn
        Store DCurC
        Load  DIAM
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt

DSOLp,  Load  Cnt
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  DSODo
        Jump  DSOEnd
DSODo,  Load  DCurR
        Subt  Uno
        Store DCurR
        Store PR
        Load  DCurC
        Subt  Uno
        Store DCurC
        Store PC
        JnS   PintarPunto
        Load  Cnt
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt
        Jump  DSOLp

/ =======================================================================
/ Lado Oesteв†’Norte: desde Oeste, dr=-1 dc=+1, DIAM-1 pasos
/ =======================================================================
DSOEnd, Load  FilaIn
        Store DCurR
        Load  ColIn
        Subt  DIAM
        Store DCurC
        Load  DIAM
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt

DONLp,  Load  Cnt
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  DONDo
        Jump  DONEnd
DONDo,  Load  DCurR
        Subt  Uno
        Store DCurR
        Store PR
        Load  DCurC
        Add   Uno
        Store DCurC
        Store PC
        JnS   PintarPunto
        Load  Cnt
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt
        Jump  DONLp

DONEnd, Load  CntSegInicial
        Store CntSeg
MineEnd, JumpI ColocarMinas

/ =======================================================================
/ Subrutina PintarPunto: coloca mina en (PR, PC) con wrap toroidal
/ Si PR < 0  в†’ PR += 16   |  Si PR > 15 в†’ PR -= 16
/ Si PC < 0  в†’ PC += 16   |  Si PC > 15 в†’ PC -= 16
/ =======================================================================
PintarPunto, HEX 0

        / --- Wrap fila PR ---
        Load  PR
        SkipCond 000           / PR < 0?
        Jump  PPRpos
        Load  PR
        Add   Diezseis         / PR += 16
        Store PR
        Jump  PPRchkHi
PPRpos, Load  PR               / PR >= 0: chequear limite alto
PPRchkHi, Subt Quince          / PR - 15
        SkipCond 800           / PR > 15?
        Jump  PPRok            / PR <= 15 в†’ ok
        Load  PR
        Subt  Diezseis         / PR -= 16
        Store PR

        / --- Wrap columna PC ---
PPRok,  Load  PC
        SkipCond 000           / PC < 0?
        Jump  PPCpos
        Load  PC
        Add   Diezseis         / PC += 16
        Store PC
        Jump  PPCchkHi
PPCpos, Load  PC
PPCchkHi, Subt Quince          / PC - 15
        SkipCond 800           / PC > 15?
        Jump  PPCok            / PC <= 15 в†’ ok
        Load  PC
        Subt  Diezseis         / PC -= 16
        Store PC

        / idx = PR * 16 + PC
PPCok,  Load  PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PR
        Add   PC
        Add   TablBase
        Store MinePtr
        Load  MinaVal
        StoreI MinePtr
        JumpI PintarPunto

DecrG,  Load  Cnt
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt
        Jump  PintaG
DecrR,  Load  Cnt
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt
        Jump  RevMin
DecrT,  Load  Cnt
        Subt  Uno
        Store Cnt
        Jump  PintaT


/ в”Ђв”Ђ No es mina: color segun distancia (0-8) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
NoesMina, Load ValCelda
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  EsN1
        Load  GrisC        / 0 vecinos: gris claro
        Jump  PintarCelda
EsN1,   Load  ValCelda
        Subt  Uno
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  EsN2
        Load  C1           / 1: azul
        Jump  PintarCelda
EsN2,   Load  ValCelda
        Subt  Dos
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  EsN3
        Load  C2           / 2: verde
        Jump  PintarCelda
EsN3,   Load  ValCelda
        Subt  Tres
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  EsN4
        Load  C3           / 3: rojo
        Jump  PintarCelda
EsN4,   Load  ValCelda
        Subt  Cuatro
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  EsN5
        Load  C4           / 4: azul oscuro
        Jump  PintarCelda
EsN5,   Load  ValCelda
        Subt  Cinco
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  EsN6
        Load  C5           / 5: rojo oscuro
        Jump  PintarCelda
EsN6,   Load  ValCelda
        Subt  Seis
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  EsN7
        Load  C6           / 6: turquesa
        Jump  PintarCelda
EsN7,   Load  ValCelda
        Subt  Siete
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  EsN8
        Load  C7           / 7: violeta
        Jump  PintarCelda
EsN8,   Load  C8           / 8: blanco

PintarCelda, StoreI DispPtr

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Marcar descubierta (val+100), decrementar seguras в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Load  ValCelda
        Add   MarcaDesc
        StoreI TablPtr
        Load  CntSeg
        Subt  Uno
        Store CntSeg

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Si era vacia (val==0) lanzar flood fill в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Load  ValCelda
        SkipCond 400       / si val==0 в†’ flood fill
        Jump  ContarMov    / val!=0 в†’ contar mov y verificar victoria
        Jump  IniFlood

/ в”Ђв”Ђ FLOOD FILL: columna inicial, luego wave por columnas в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
IniFlood, Load  Idx
        Store FloodOrig

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Fase 1: subir por la columna в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Load  FloodOrig
        Store CurIdx
SubirLoop, Load CurIdx
        Subt  Diezseis     / CurIdx - 16
        SkipCond 000       / AC < 0 в†’ fuera de tablero, parar
        Jump  FinSubir
        Store CurIdx       / AC >= 0 в†’ guardar nuevo CurIdx
        Load  CurIdx
        Add   TablBase
        Store WTPtr        / puntero a tablero[CurIdx]
        Load  CurIdx
        Add   DispBase
        Store WDPtr        / puntero a display[CurIdx]
        LoadI WDPtr        / color actual
        Subt  Gris         / es gris (oculto)?
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  FinSubir     / no es gris в†’ parar
        LoadI WTPtr        / val = tablero[CurIdx]
        Store WVal
        Add   Uno          / val+1: si era mina в†’ 0
        SkipCond 800       / AC > 0 в†’ no es mina
        Jump  FinSubir     / es mina в†’ parar
        JnS   PintaColor   / pinta WVal en WDPtr
        Load  WVal
        Add   MarcaDesc
        StoreI WTPtr       / marcar tablero+100
        Load  CntSeg
        Subt  Uno
        Store CntSeg
        Load  WVal
        SkipCond 400       / si WVal==0 в†’ era vacia в†’ seguir subiendo
        Jump  FinSubir     / era numero в†’ parar
        Jump  SubirLoop
FinSubir, Load  Cero

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Fase 2: bajar por la columna в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Load  FloodOrig
        Store CurIdx
BajarLoop, Load CurIdx
        Add   Diezseis     / CurIdx + 16
        Store CurIdx
        Subt  MaxIdx       / AC = CurIdx - 256
        SkipCond 000       / AC < 0 в†’ valido (CurIdx < 256)
        Jump  FinBajar     / CurIdx >= 256 в†’ fuera de tablero
        Load  CurIdx
        Add   TablBase
        Store WTPtr
        Load  CurIdx
        Add   DispBase
        Store WDPtr
        LoadI WDPtr        / color actual
        Subt  Gris
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  FinBajar     / no es gris в†’ parar
        LoadI WTPtr
        Store WVal
        Add   Uno
        SkipCond 800
        Jump  FinBajar     / es mina в†’ parar
        JnS   PintaColor
        Load  WVal
        Add   MarcaDesc
        StoreI WTPtr
        Load  CntSeg
        Subt  Uno
        Store CntSeg
        Load  WVal
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  FinBajar     / era numero в†’ parar
        Jump  BajarLoop
FinBajar, Load  Cero

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Fase 3: wave por columnas (WC exterior, WR interior) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        LoadImmi 1
        Store FFChg        / FFChg=1 para entrar al while

FFWLOOP, Load  FFChg
        SkipCond 800       / FFChg > 0 в†’ continuar
        Jump  ContarMov    / FFChg == 0 в†’ fin flood в†’ contar mov
        Clear
        Store FFChg        / reset FFChg
        Clear
        Store WC           / WC = 0 (columna)

/ в”Ђв”Ђ for WC = 0 to 15 (columnas) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
FFCLOOP, Load  WC
        Subt  Diezseis
        SkipCond 000       / WC < 16 в†’ continuar
        Jump  FFWLOOP      / WC >= 16 в†’ nueva ola
        Clear
        Store WR           / WR = 0 (fila)

/ в”Ђв”Ђ for WR = 0 to 15 (filas) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
FFRLOOP, Load  WR
        Subt  Diezseis
        SkipCond 000       / WR < 16 в†’ continuar
        Jump  FFINCC       / WR >= 16 в†’ siguiente columna

/ в”Ђв”Ђ WIDX = WR * 16 + WC в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Load  WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WR
        Add   WC
        Store WIDX

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Si display[WIDX] == GrisC в†’ celda vacia revelada в†’ propagar в”Ђ
        Load  WIDX
        Add   DispBase
        Store WDPtr
        LoadI WDPtr
        Subt  GrisC
        SkipCond 400       / display == GrisC?
        Jump  FFINCR       / no в†’ siguiente fila

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Propagar a los 8 vecinos в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        / Vecino (-1,-1)
        Load  WR
        Subt  Uno
        Store NR
        Load  WC
        Subt  Uno
        Store NC
        JnS   FFRVNGH

        / Vecino (-1,+0)
        Load  WR
        Subt  Uno
        Store NR
        Load  WC
        Store NC
        JnS   FFRVNGH

        / Vecino (-1,+1)
        Load  WR
        Subt  Uno
        Store NR
        Load  WC
        Add   Uno
        Store NC
        JnS   FFRVNGH

        / Vecino (+0,-1)
        Load  WR
        Store NR
        Load  WC
        Subt  Uno
        Store NC
        JnS   FFRVNGH

        / Vecino (+0,+1)
        Load  WR
        Store NR
        Load  WC
        Add   Uno
        Store NC
        JnS   FFRVNGH

        / Vecino (+1,-1)
        Load  WR
        Add   Uno
        Store NR
        Load  WC
        Subt  Uno
        Store NC
        JnS   FFRVNGH

        / Vecino (+1,+0)
        Load  WR
        Add   Uno
        Store NR
        Load  WC
        Store NC
        JnS   FFRVNGH

        / Vecino (+1,+1)
        Load  WR
        Add   Uno
        Store NR
        Load  WC
        Add   Uno
        Store NC
        JnS   FFRVNGH

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Incrementar WR в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
FFINCR, Load  WR
        Add   Uno
        Store WR
        Jump  FFRLOOP

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Incrementar WC в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
FFINCC, Load  WC
        Add   Uno
        Store WC
        Jump  FFCLOOP

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Subrutina FFRVNGH в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
FFRVNGH, HEX 0
        Clear
        Store WVal         / reset WVal

        / Verificar NR >= 0
        Load  NR
        SkipCond 000       / NR < 0 в†’ salir
        Jump  FFRV1
        JumpI FFRVNGH
FFRV1,  Load  NR           / Verificar NR < 16
        Subt  Diezseis
        SkipCond 000
        JumpI FFRVNGH
        Load  NC           / Verificar NC >= 0
        SkipCond 000
        Jump  FFRV2
        JumpI FFRVNGH
FFRV2,  Load  NC           / Verificar NC < 16
        Subt  Diezseis
        SkipCond 000
        JumpI FFRVNGH

        / NIDX = NR*16 + NC
        Load  NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NR
        Add   NC
        Store NIDX

        / Verificar display[NIDX] == Gris (oculto sin bandera)
        Load  NIDX
        Add   DispBase
        Store WDPtr
        LoadI WDPtr
        Subt  Gris
        SkipCond 400
        JumpI FFRVNGH

        / Verificar no es mina: tablero[NIDX]+1 > 0
        Load  NIDX
        Add   TablBase
        Store WTPtr
        LoadI WTPtr
        Store WVal
        Add   Uno
        SkipCond 800       / AC > 0 в†’ no es mina
        JumpI FFRVNGH

        / Pintar color correcto via subrutina compartida
        JnS   PintaColor   / usa WVal, pinta en WDPtr
        Load  WVal
        Add   MarcaDesc
        StoreI WTPtr       / marcar tablero+100
        Load  CntSeg
        Subt  Uno
        Store CntSeg
        LoadImmi 1
        Store FFChg        / hubo cambio
        JumpI FFRVNGH

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Subrutina PintaColor: despacha color segun WVal в†’ pinta WDPtr
PintaColor, HEX 0
        Load  WVal
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  PC_N1
        Load  GrisC
        Jump  PC_PINTA
PC_N1,  Load  WVal
        Subt  Uno
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  PC_N2
        Load  C1
        Jump  PC_PINTA
PC_N2,  Load  WVal
        Subt  Dos
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  PC_N3
        Load  C2
        Jump  PC_PINTA
PC_N3,  Load  WVal
        Subt  Tres
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  PC_N4
        Load  C3
        Jump  PC_PINTA
PC_N4,  Load  WVal
        Subt  Cuatro
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  PC_N5
        Load  C4
        Jump  PC_PINTA
PC_N5,  Load  WVal
        Subt  Cinco
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  PC_N6
        Load  C5
        Jump  PC_PINTA
PC_N6,  Load  WVal
        Subt  Seis
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  PC_N7
        Load  C6
        Jump  PC_PINTA
PC_N7,  Load  WVal
        Subt  Siete
        SkipCond 400
        Jump  PC_N8
        Load  C7
        Jump  PC_PINTA
PC_N8,  Load  C8
PC_PINTA, StoreI WDPtr
        JumpI PintaColor

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Contar movimiento y verificar victoria в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
ContarMov, Load  Movimientos
        Add   Uno
        Store Movimientos  / Movimientos++
        Load  CntSeg
        SkipCond 400       / CntSeg == 0 в†’ ganaste
        Jump  Turno        / CntSeg != 0 в†’ siguiente turno
        JnS   PrintMsgGana / OUTPUT: 'Ganaste!'
        Load  Movimientos
        Output             / score final al ganar
        Load  CharNL
        Output
        Halt               / FIN: ganaste

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Variables в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
FilaIn,      DEC 0
ColIn,       DEC 0
Accion,      DEC 0
Idx,         DEC 0
Ptr,         DEC 0
TablPtr,     DEC 0
DispPtr,     DEC 0
DispPtr2,    DEC 0
ValCelda,    DEC 0
ValTemp,     DEC 0
CntSeg,      DEC 0
Cnt,         DEC 0
Movimientos, DEC 0
FloodOrig,   DEC 0
CurIdx,      DEC 0
FFChg,       DEC 0
WR,          DEC 0
WC,          DEC 0
WIDX,        DEC 0
WDPtr,       DEC 0
WTPtr,       DEC 0
WVal,        DEC 0
NR,          DEC 0
NC,          DEC 0
NIDX,        DEC 0
Seguras,     DEC 253
TablBase,    HEX 400
DispBase,    HEX 0F00
MarcaDesc,   DEC 100
MarcaBand,   DEC 200
MinaBand,    DEC 199
Cero,        DEC 0
Uno,         DEC 1
Dos,         DEC 2
Tres,        DEC 3
Cuatro,      DEC 4
Cinco,       DEC 5
Seis,        DEC 6
Siete,       DEC 7
Diezseis,    DEC 16
MaxIdx,      DEC 256
Gris,        HEX 294A     / gris oscuro: oculta
GrisC,       HEX 6318     / gris claro: 0 vecinos
Negro,       HEX 0000     / negro: mina
Amarillo,    HEX 5E65     / amarillo: bandera
C1,          HEX 1DB5     / azul
C2,          HEX 1E29     / verde
C3,          HEX 654A     / rojo
C4,          HEX 0CCD     / azul oscuro
C5,          HEX 3484     / rojo oscuro
C6,          HEX 1631     / turquesa
C7,          HEX 34F3     / violeta
C8,          HEX 6B5A     / blanco
ImpVal,      DEC 0        / variable aux ImprimirNum
ImpDig,      DEC 0        / variable aux ImprimirNum
ImpFlag,     DEC 0        / variable aux ImprimirNum
Ascii0,      DEC 48       / codigo ASCII de '0'
Cien,        DEC 100
Diez,        DEC 10
/ --- Variables nuevas (rombo Manhattan) ---
DIAM,       DEC 0
DCurR,      DEC 0
DCurC,      DEC 0
PR,         DEC 0
PC,         DEC 0
MinePtr,    HEX 400
MinaVal,    DEC -1
MineMax,    HEX 500
MineWrap,   HEX 100
Quince,     DEC 15
CntSegInicial, DEC 247          / fijar segГєn forma antes de ensamblar
/ в”Ђв”Ђ Subrutina ImprimirNum: imprime Movimientos en ASCII в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
/ Imprime hasta 3 digitos (0-999). No imprime ceros a la izquierda.
/ Usa variables: ImpVal, ImpDig, ImpFlag
ImprimirNum, HEX 0
        Load  Movimientos
        Store ImpVal       / ImpVal = Movimientos
        Clear
        Store ImpFlag      / ImpFlag=0: aun no imprimimos ningun digito
/ в”Ђв”Ђ Centenas в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
        Clear
        Store ImpDig       / ImpDig = 0 (contador de centenas)
ImpC,   Load  ImpVal
        Subt  Cien
        SkipCond 800       / AC > 0 в†’ ImpVal >= 100
        Jump  ImpCFin      / ImpVal < 100 в†’ fin centenas
        Store ImpVal       / ImpVal -= 100
        Load  ImpDig
        Add   Uno
        Store ImpDig
        Jump  ImpC
ImpCFin, Load  ImpDig
        SkipCond 400       / ImpDig == 0 в†’ no imprimir
        Jump  ImpCSkip     / ImpDig != 0 в†’ imprimir centena
        Jump  ImpD         / ImpDig == 0 в†’ saltar a decenas
ImpCSkip, Load  ImpDig
        Add   Ascii0       / digito + '0'
        Output
        LoadImmi 1
        Store ImpFlag      / ya imprimimos algo
/ в”Ђв”Ђ Decenas в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
ImpD,   Clear
        Store ImpDig
ImpD2,  Load  ImpVal
        Subt  Diez
        SkipCond 800       / AC > 0 в†’ ImpVal >= 10
        Jump  ImpDFin
        Store ImpVal
        Load  ImpDig
        Add   Uno
        Store ImpDig
        Jump  ImpD2
ImpDFin, Load  ImpFlag
        SkipCond 400       / ImpFlag == 0 в†’ solo imprimir si ImpDig != 0
        Jump  ImpDForce    / ImpFlag != 0 в†’ imprimir siempre
        Load  ImpDig
        SkipCond 400       / ImpDig == 0 в†’ saltar
        Jump  ImpDSkip
        Jump  ImpU
ImpDForce, Load  ImpDig
        Add   Ascii0
        Output
        Jump  ImpU2
ImpDSkip, Load  ImpDig
        Add   Ascii0
        Output
        LoadImmi 1
        Store ImpFlag
/ в”Ђв”Ђ Unidades в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
ImpU,   Load  ImpVal      / lo que queda son unidades
ImpU2,  Add   Ascii0
        Output
        JumpI ImprimirNum

/ в”Ђв”Ђ Subrutinas de output Unicode в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
